ygData.messageBody:
Hello,

There is a new survey for the eqbards community.

Since the list has grown to over 150 members with some great threads, I was wondering if anyone would be interested in an ICQ chat event. Please give me your answers so we can get this together.

----

Possible answers are:

o Not Interested in a chat session
o Yes once a week
o Yes every other week
o Yes once a month
o Yes every other month


To vote, please visit the following web page:

http://www.onelist.com/surveycenter/eqbards


Thanks!

eqbards Owner
